            <title><![CDATA[0.22.0 Release]]></title>
            <link>https://botomy.vercel.app/Botomy/blog/0.22.0-release</link>
            <guid>https://botomy.vercel.app/Botomy/blog/0.22.0-release</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[New game play mechanics]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>0.22.0 Release - Cloaking</p>
<p>This release introduces a new power up - the ring!</p>
<p>This ring allows a play to cloak. Once cloaked, a player is not visible to other players or enemies.</p>
<p>Attacking will decloak.</p>
<p>Shields cannot be raised when cloaked. Cloaking will take down your shield.</p>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>releases</category>
