            <description><![CDATA[Kill reward calc in fight world]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>0.23.1 Use an equation to calc player kill reward in fight world</p>
<p>Some exponential curve as the level increases (presumably the player is harder to kill). So you get a reward up to 5x the base (120).
1 + (0.541<em>exp(0.1</em>level))</p>]]></content:encoded>
